to: html
  from: markdown+emoji
  output-file: index.html
  standalone: true
  title-prefix: Jacob Jameson
  section-divs: true
  html-math-method: mathjax
  wrap: none
  default-image-extension: png
  toc: true
  reference-location: margin
  css:
    - styles.css

document-css: false
  link-citations: true
  date-format: long
  lang: en
  twitter-card:
    creator: '@JacobCJameson'
    image: images/profile.png
    card-style: summary_large_image
  toc-location: left
  anchor-sections: true
  fig-cap-location: margin
  footnotes-hover: true
  fontsize: 1em
  theme: spacelab
  title: Links
  image: images/profile.png
  about:
    template: solana
    links:
      - icon: envelope
        text: Email
        href: jacobjameson@g.harvard.edu
      - icon: github
        text: Github
        href: 'https://github.com/jacobjameson'
      - icon: twitter
        text: Twitter
        href: 'https://twitter.com/JacobCJameson'
      - icon: linkedin
        text: LinkedIn
        href: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/jacob-jameson/'
      - icon: mortarboard
        text: CV
        href: Data/vitae.pdf
  page-layout: full
